title: Business Briefing: Bank of England Maintains Interest Rate at 0.5%.
text:
Published By: NYTimes Int. Business - Today 
The Bank of England showed no sign it was close to raising interest rates, voting on Thursday to keep them at 0.5 percent, a record low....
